Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.86,0:00:14.89,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:15.23,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:18.87,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies straight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:22.83,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows threaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:26.72,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:30.46,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:34.02,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.02,0:00:36.62,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:40.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.33,0:00:44.93,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.93,0:00:48.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:51.07,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.22,0:00:54.94,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.82,0:00:59.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.50,0:01:03.09,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:11.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato is the\NKamen Rider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.30,0:01:15.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil Shocker, a secret\Norganization plotting world domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.10,0:01:18.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to fight\NShocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.19,0:01:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, isn't it pretty?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.08,0:01:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna pick more...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.63,0:01:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go too far.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.30,0:01:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.23,0:01:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now. It's just a frog.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.17,0:01:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He should be here by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.03,0:01:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, who are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.88,0:01:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come along, Rumiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.70,0:01:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:56.97,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,190.389)}Japan in Peril!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:56.97,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(497.167,680.389)}Gamagiller's Invasion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.16,0:02:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Are you Ichimonji Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.09,0:02:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I need help from you... and by\Nthat, I mean the Kamen Rider.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:18.07,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\3c&H3D2D01&\c&H68A2BB&\fs55}Origuchi Institute of\NCrime Research
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.80,0:02:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I know about Shocker, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.81,0:02:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking into Shocker's activities,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.99,0:02:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,when I stumbled upon\Na terrible plan in the works.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.32,0:02:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay close by, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.39,0:02:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but feel\Nlike someone's after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.29,0:02:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.27,0:03:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good. Damn that Hayato...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This area, Kurobe Gorge,\Nis Japan's weakest geological point.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.87,0:03:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The east and west sides have\Ncompletely different geological makeups.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Our plan to cause a nuclear explosion here,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,tear the land in two,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.33,0:03:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and take over Japan in the ensuing\Nchaos is proceeding smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The special nuclear bomb will\Narrive from the homeland
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,to our secret airfield\Nbefore the day is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But how do you explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.94,0:03:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,your inability to kidnap the daughter\Nof Origuchi, who's caught on to our plan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He was on guard for a\Nkidnapping while he was outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.25,0:03:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't get close.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.88,0:03:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Gamagiller, test out your nerve gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring a prisoner here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.54,0:04:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it... let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.19,0:04:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.78,0:04:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.36,0:04:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No one would ever believe\Na word a man like that said.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.62,0:04:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,First, take his daughter hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then see to it that he can\Nnever reveal Shocker's secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.05,0:05:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.07,0:05:04.32,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\an7\3c&H3D2D01&\c&H68A2BB&\fs55}Origuchi Institute of\NCrime Research
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.63,0:05:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, go to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.07,0:05:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:21.12,Italics,,0,0,0,,No one may enter without\Nan appointment in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.12,0:05:22.33,Italics,,0,0,0,,Please leave at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:25.59,Italics,,0,0,0,,Recognize that I've taken\Nyour picture as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn... his security is airtight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.15,0:05:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,All right... go around behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the proof that they're still\Nhanging around the estate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My assistant let her play in the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.25,0:05:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you certain that's safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. No one can enter the yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be fine, as long as\Nshe doesn't leave the grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.12,0:05:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.45,0:05:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You hit it too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where it went...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumiko! Did you find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Not here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro, you're here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me guess.\N"What am I going to do?" Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yes, actually.\N- I figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't bring any for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally we'd treat you first, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.07,0:07:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're a big boy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem! I've got...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.38,0:07:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Look? I'm gonna stick it on you!\NSee? I'll stick it on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.27,0:07:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stick it on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.07,0:07:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go home, froggie dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, all for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.73,0:07:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro was so mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's eating it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.21,0:07:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll stick it on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we have these?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.03,0:07:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just whose side are you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we bought those, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.84,0:07:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better pay us back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:07:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Phone for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,From who?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask them yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No fury like a woman starved, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.18,0:08:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.97,0:08:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hayato?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.38,0:08:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? A frog monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Shocker again?\N- A frog?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Origuchi, try to stay strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This file is what Shocker is after.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no question they'll\Nask for it in exchange for Rumiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'd even arranged a witness...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to tell the world\Nabout Shocker's evils!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.82,0:08:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do anything\Nwhile she's their hostage!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the witness?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The survivor of a four-man expedition\Nin the Alps that was attacked by Shocker.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.14,0:08:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She apparently heard the word\Nof their plan to split Japan in two
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,from the mouth of their leader himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.70,0:08:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,From their leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.08,0:09:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... she met their leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but she lost her\Nmemory right after,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.33,0:09:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and now all she has is the vague\Nmemory of having seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But... if I could just project her\Nmemories onto this brainwave screen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we'd get an\Nimage of their leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.01,0:09:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.82,0:10:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you'd come, Ichimonji Hayato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Take her away, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Transform!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.12,0:11:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... we'll meet again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.78,0:12:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the way in?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:43.20,Bumper Episode 14-51,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs85\pos(311,454)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.30,0:12:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.78,0:12:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What an awful way\Nto treat such a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.54,0:13:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the girl to an underground cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider, there you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.52,0:13:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- Let's get out of here!\N- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how they\Nplan to conquer the wo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.80,0:14:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.50,0:14:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.46,0:14:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the men who saved Rumiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Really... you did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.01,0:14:17.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumiko... I'm so glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,- Papa!\N- Rumiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This way! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hope this machine\Ncan relay her memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, try.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.59,0:14:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.50,0:14:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Slowly and calmly,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.40,0:15:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,remember what happened\Nwhen you met Shocker's leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to focus your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see something...\Nbut I don't know where I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.70,0:15:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is where I woke up, after\Nfalling into that cave in the Andes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You found yourself inside Shocker's cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I lost consciousness again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hours passed, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Days passed, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.90,0:15:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you found yourself\Nstanding in front of a strange door...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I could hear someone\Ngiving orders beyond it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.79,0:15:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Then someone else, calling them "leader."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:16:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you open that door?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.63,0:16:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I just peeked in through the crack...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw it, didn't you?\NYou saw the identity of their leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.60,0:16:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I did see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.11,0:16:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It gave some kind of order.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.31,0:16:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What did it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.73,0:16:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it said...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"Go to the secret airfield in Tokyo."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Secret airfield?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,At 3 o'clock on October 10th,\Nwe'll transport the nuclear bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.66,0:16:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not let anyone find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.79,0:16:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,October 10th?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.26,0:16:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Try harder! Kinuko, you're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see him clearly now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm remembering...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.57,0:17:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,- Kinuko! Kinuko!\N- Kinuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.72,0:17:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.38,0:17:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker's on their way in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Take Kinuko to safety, to the second floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.22,0:17:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this, you monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.36,0:17:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought I'd have\Nto use this system,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but Shocker will make fine guinea pigs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.98,0:17:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.49,0:18:25.76,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&}Crime Investigation Report\NOriguchi Crime Research Institute
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.95,0:18:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, stay alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.41,0:18:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.45,0:18:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Finish them off!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.34,0:19:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Unload the bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the nuclear bomb in question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.27,0:20:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It has the power to tear Japan in two!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.94,0:20:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Give my regards to Colonel Zol.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Gamagiller, this is it.\NWe're counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.04,0:20:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you,\NGamagiller? Kill him at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.39,0:21:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.37,0:21:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider... catch me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.97,0:21:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What now, Rider?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.24,0:21:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.46,0:22:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing personal, but we'd\Nbetter go our separate ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.36,0:22:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.65,0:22:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.30,0:22:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.48,0:22:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we can eat ice\Ncream without fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.41,0:22:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.32,0:22:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Rumiko! Let's go catch another frog!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.10,0:22:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't like frogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.01,0:22:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you want ice cream,\NI'll happily join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.42,0:22:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- Yeah, let's go.\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.70,0:22:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're better.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.90,0:22:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you lost your memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.39,0:22:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's a good thing that\Nyou forgot your traumatic past.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:23:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave future battles with Shocker to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.72,0:23:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.13,0:23:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I don't remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.82,0:23:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be mean, Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.15,0:23:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This man saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.85,0:23:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.40,0:23:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But, is Shocker real?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.95,0:23:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better if you don't\Nknow, Mr. Origuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.73,0:23:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.83,0:23:30.04,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In the end, Shocker's evils\Nremained unrevealed to the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.04,0:23:33.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,because Kinuko and Origuchi\Nhad both lost their memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.11,0:23:37.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But Ichimonji Hayato's battle\Nagainst Shocker would continue!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.23,0:23:40.83,Cont,,0,50,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.15,0:23:43.65,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.15,0:23:44.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.23,0:23:47.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the killer queen ant, Arichimedes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.48,0:23:49.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Colonel Zol plans to conquer Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.66,0:23:51.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,using the formic acid\Nshe spits from her antennae.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.95,0:23:54.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ichimonji Hayato and his\Nallies stand in her way.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.80,0:24:01.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for "The\NKiller Queen Ant, Arichimedes."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.18,0:24:00.74,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs135\fscy95\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(507.167,730.389)}The Killer Queen Ant \NArichimedes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.13,0:24:09.97,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.55,0:24:12.55,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.55,0:24:14.51,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.51,0:24:17.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the villains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.06,0:24:19.93,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.93,0:24:21.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.81,0:24:23.60,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.60,0:24:25.05,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.40,0:24:27.19,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.47,0:24:33.16,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with all of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.16,0:24:36.74,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.74,0:24:40.75,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.75,0:24:45.27,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan in Peril!\NGamagiller's Invasion